{"title":"Vue项目杂记","uid":"a6ceee259e52c26d7785e67e6f455bb5","slug":"Vue项目杂记","date":"2024-04-08T12:41:00.000Z","updated":"2024-04-08T13:00:48.813Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Vue项目杂记.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/photo-15.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"Vue项目的运行\"><a href=\"#Vue项目的运行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vue项目的运行\"></a>Vue项目的运行</h1><h2 id=\"搭建环境\"><a href=\"#搭建环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搭建环境\"></a>搭建环境</h2><ol>\n<li><p><strong>node</strong> 的安装</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>npm</strong> 的安装&amp;设置镜像</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>随后在安装目录下输入命令，安装项目依赖的库：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>例如在 <code>jiazheng-banner</code> 项目中，我们需要移动到<code>jiazheng-banner-web</code> ，也就是前端所在的位置中，然后再进行安装命令。</p>\n<p>如果是<strong>vue3+vite</strong>的话，可以直接运行一下命令启动项目</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm run dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h1 id=\"关于如何添加新的Vue页面\"><a href=\"#关于如何添加新的Vue页面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"关于如何添加新的Vue页面\"></a>关于如何添加新的Vue页面</h1><p>涉及关键词：Vue路由、添加新页面、页面跳转</p>\n<p>在 <code>jiazheng-banner</code> 项目中</p>\n<p>首先是先在 <code>router</code> 文件夹下 找到 <code>index.js</code> 和 <code>root.js</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"index-js\"><a href=\"#index-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"index.js\"></a>index.js</h2><p>先添加登录验证，直接Copy上面的代码就行了</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/** 帮助页面路由 **/</span><br><span class=\"line\">  if (to.path.startsWith(&#x27;/Help&#x27;)) &#123; </span><br><span class=\"line\">  // 主要修改上面一行，根据你创建的文件夹</span><br><span class=\"line\">  // 我的是 src/views/Help</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if (localStorage.getItem(USER_TOKEN)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      if (to.path === loginRoutePath) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        next(&#123; path: &#x27;/&#x27; &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        next()</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      if (allowList.includes(to.name)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        // 在免登录名单，直接进入</span><br><span class=\"line\">        next()</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        next(&#123; path: loginRoutePath, query: &#123; redirect: to.fullPath &#125; &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    // next()</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>其他设置不用动</p>\n<h2 id=\"root-js\"><a href=\"#root-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"root.js\"></a>root.js</h2><p>然后再在 <code>root.js</code> 里面添加路径</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">//  帮助页</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    path: &#x27;/Help&#x27;, // 你的文件夹名称</span><br><span class=\"line\">    name: &#x27;Help&#x27;,  // 随便起个名字方便记忆</span><br><span class=\"line\">    component: () =&gt; import(&#x27;/@/views/Help/help.vue&#x27;), </span><br><span class=\"line\">    // 这里就是你写的页面所在的路径，貌似不区分大小写</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"help-vue\"><a href=\"#help-vue\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"help.vue\"></a>help.vue</h2><p>这个就是vue格式的页面了，具体看你自己想怎么写</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 仅仅是个我让AI写的测试页</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;template&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;h1&gt;&#123;&#123; message &#125;&#125;&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;button @click=&quot;changeMessage&quot;&gt;Change Message&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/template&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">export default &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  data() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      message: &#x27;Hello, Vue!&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  methods: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    changeMessage() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      this.message = &#x27;Vue is awesome!&#x27;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;style&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">h1 &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  color: blue;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">button &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  background-color: lightblue;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  border: none;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  padding: 10px 20px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  cursor: pointer;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  border-radius: 5px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/style&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"a-标签跳转\"><a href=\"#a-标签跳转\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"a 标签跳转\"></a>a 标签跳转</h2><p>最后在 <code>系统文档</code> 处的a标签中，设置即可，具体代码如下:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;a href=&quot;/Help&quot; class=&quot;foot-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;系统文档&lt;/a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>PS：target 决定了跳转方式</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>值</th>\n<th>描述</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>_blank</td>\n<td>在新窗口中打开被链接文档。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>_self</td>\n<td>默认。在相同的框架中打开被链接文档。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>_parent</td>\n<td>在父框架集中打开被链接文档。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>_top</td>\n<td>在整个窗口中打开被链接文档。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><em>framename</em></td>\n<td>在指定的框架中打开被链接文档。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h1 id=\"关于商品标签分类\"><a href=\"#关于商品标签分类\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"关于商品标签分类\"></a>关于商品标签分类</h1><p>涉及关键词：数据表关系的分析、后端与数据库交互、前端页面交互、根据关键值控制商品的分类</p>\n<p>从MySQL数据库中，可以得知 <strong>商品标签的添加</strong> 由 <strong>b_thing_tag</strong> 这个表控制，又因为MySQL是关系型数据库。所以关联的还有 <strong>b_thing</strong>、<strong>b_tag</strong> 这两个表。</p>\n<p>所以，一旦需要在HTML标签中添加分类功能，那我们需要在JavaScript中同时调用这三个库的数据进行处理，并撰写对应的逻辑。</p>\n<h2 id=\"前端代码\"><a href=\"#前端代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前端代码\"></a>前端代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;translators flex-view&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">style</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">   <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>分类：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">   <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;name&quot;</span>&gt;</span>&#123;&#123; getCategoryName(detailData.classificationId) &#125;&#125;<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"后端代码\"><a href=\"#后端代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"后端代码\"></a>后端代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"title function_\">getCategoryName</span> =(<span class=\"params\">classificationId</span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> categories = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"number\">1</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;服装&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"number\">2</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;零食&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"number\">3</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;图书&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"number\">4</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;儿童玩具&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"number\">5</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;厨房用品&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"number\">6</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;电器&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"number\">7</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;办公用品&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> categories[classificationId];</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"核心原理\"><a href=\"#核心原理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"核心原理\"></a>核心原理</h2><p>理论上无非就是获取 detailData对象的所有属性，直接F12可以在控制台（console）中看到打印的对象，他能从后端返回什么属性，就可以提取到前端。</p>\n<p>但<strong>classificationID</strong>本身是数字，他在<strong>b_classification</strong>表中对应了7个标签。原则上讲，我们应该从后端调用过来，用类似for的方法遍历<strong>b_classification</strong>表，但是基于我的水平太差，我直接写7个标签让他一一对应（类似switch case）。</p>\n<h1 id=\"关于商品上下架问题\"><a href=\"#关于商品上下架问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"关于商品上下架问题\"></a>关于商品上下架问题</h1><p>涉及关键词：后端与数据库交互、前端页面交互、根据关键值控制商品上下架、数据过滤、分页逻辑、隐藏商品后页面留空（铺不满）</p>\n<h2 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h2><p>根据F12控制台大致得知，控制商品上下架的核心参数，是<strong>b_thing</strong>表里面的<strong>status</strong>这个参数控制，大意是<strong>1为下架，0为上架</strong>，但并没有具体的代码逻辑去根据他这个参数来控制上下架，所以需要自己写，应该可以在前端 detali.vue里面写。</p>\n<h2 id=\"解决方案\"><a href=\"#解决方案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决方案\"></a>解决方案</h2><p>在经历过废案后，我思考了，隐藏商品的逻辑应该写在JavaScript里面，而不是单纯的调用v-show进行片面的隐藏。于是乎我找到了各大AI帮我解决问题，最终在Coze中找到了问题的解决方案。</p>\n<p>结果如下：</p>\n<p>源代码为：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 分页事件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"title function_\">changePage</span> = (<span class=\"params\">page</span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   contentData.<span class=\"property\">page</span> = page</span><br><span class=\"line\">   <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> start = (contentData.<span class=\"property\">page</span> - <span class=\"number\">1</span>) * contentData.<span class=\"property\">pageSize</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">   contentData.<span class=\"property\">pageData</span> = contentData.<span class=\"property\">thingData</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">slice</span>(start, start + contentData.<span class=\"property\">pageSize</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">   <span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;第&#x27;</span> + contentData.<span class=\"property\">page</span> + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;页&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>更改后的代码为：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"title function_\">changePage</span> = (<span class=\"params\">page</span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  contentData.<span class=\"property\">page</span> = page;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">//首先，计算所有未下架商品的列表</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> allAvailableItems = contentData.<span class=\"property\">thingData</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">filter</span>(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"params\">item</span> =&gt;</span> item.<span class=\"property\">status</span> !== <span class=\"string\">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">//计算要在当前页显示的起始索引和结束索引（考虑到未下架的商品）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> start = (contentData.<span class=\"property\">page</span> - <span class=\"number\">1</span>) * contentData.<span class=\"property\">pageSize</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> end = start + contentData.<span class=\"property\">pageSize</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">//切片出当前页应显示的商品列表（保证它们都未下架）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  contentData.<span class=\"property\">pageData</span> = allAvailableItems.<span class=\"title function_\">slice</span>(start, end);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">//根据过滤后的结果，计算出应显示的实际商品数量</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (contentData.<span class=\"property\">pageData</span>.<span class=\"property\">length</span> &lt; contentData.<span class=\"property\">pageSize</span> &amp;&amp; end &lt; allAvailableItems.<span class=\"property\">length</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    contentData.<span class=\"property\">pageData</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">push</span>(allAvailableItems[end]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    end++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 更新总的可用项目数量，以便翻页控件可以正确显示页面数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  contentData.<span class=\"property\">total</span> = allAvailableItems.<span class=\"property\">length</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;第&#x27;</span> + contentData.<span class=\"property\">page</span> + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;页&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>上述代码的重点在于，在分页逻辑中，<strong>确保不再基于全部商品数量来分页，而是基于过滤后（即非下架商品）的数量来分页，同时在生成每页数据时，确保没有留空。</strong></p>\n<p>因为<strong>我是想让下一页面的商品来填充当前页面</strong>，所以在代码逻辑中，<strong>需要修改的是翻页处理的逻辑，而不是数据过滤的逻辑</strong>，确保在当前页显示满足条件的商品数量。如果当前页的商品数未满，您需要从后续的页数中提前取出一些商品来填充当前页面。</p>\n<p>另外我把原来部分JavaScript和HTML的代码整合到了changePage中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">v-for</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;item in filteredPageData&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">:key</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;item.id&quot;</span> @<span class=\"attr\">click</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;handleDetail(item)&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">              <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;thing-item item-column-3&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> filteredPageData = <span class=\"title function_\">computed</span>(<span class=\"function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> contentData.<span class=\"property\">pageData</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">filter</span>(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"params\">item</span> =&gt;</span> item.<span class=\"property\">status</span> !== <span class=\"string\">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"废弃方案\"><a href=\"#废弃方案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"废弃方案\"></a>废弃方案</h2><p><strong>v-if 判断（同 if ）、v-show （隐藏&#x2F;显示)</strong></p>\n<p>直接在前端里面（本项目content.vue页面中）找到对应的渲染标签，使用<strong>v-show</strong>写一个逻辑即可，原本应该使用<strong>v-if</strong>的，但<strong>v-if</strong>不能和<strong>v-for</strong>混用，所以只能使用<strong>v-show</strong>，具体代码如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">v-for</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;item in contentData.pageData&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">:key</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;item.id&quot;</span>  <span class=\"attr\">click</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;handleDetail(item)&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">v-show</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;item.status!==&#x27;1&#x27;&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">      <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;thing-item item-column-3&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>核心代码其实就一行：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">v-show=&quot;item.status!==&#x27;1&#x27;&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>上述方案看似有效，但实际上会出现隐藏后留空的问题。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">v-show 隐藏下架的商品后，本身渲染给div的位置并不会消失，这是待解决的问题。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">大佬说，这跟 v-show 无关，应该去看看 v-for 里面的key是怎么定义的，页面本身是怎么渲染的。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"衍生问题-隐藏后页面依旧可访问\"><a href=\"#衍生问题-隐藏后页面依旧可访问\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"衍生问题 - 隐藏后页面依旧可访问\"></a>衍生问题 - 隐藏后页面依旧可访问</h2><p>直接通过地址去访问被隐藏的商品，依旧可以正常操作，这也是待解决的问题</p>\n<p>这个应该可以通过前端另外的逻辑去解决这个问题</p>\n<h1 id=\"未完待续…\"><a href=\"#未完待续…\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"未完待续…\"></a>未完待续…</h1>","feature":true,"text":"关于对于Vue3+SpringBoot的项目中的一些杂七杂八的记录......","permalink":"/post/Vue项目杂记","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.8k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"study","slug":"study","count":7,"path":"api/categories/study.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"个人建站","slug":"个人建站","count":6,"path":"api/tags/个人建站.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Vue%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Vue项目的运行</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">搭建环境</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84Vue%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">关于如何添加新的Vue页面</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#index-js\"><span class=\"toc-text\">index.js</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#root-js\"><span class=\"toc-text\">root.js</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#help-vue\"><span class=\"toc-text\">help.vue</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#a-%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E8%B7%B3%E8%BD%AC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">a 标签跳转</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">关于商品标签分类</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">前端代码</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">后端代码</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">核心原理</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">关于商品上下架问题</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">前言</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">解决方案</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BA%9F%E5%BC%83%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">废弃方案</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A1%8D%E7%94%9F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-%E9%9A%90%E8%97%8F%E5%90%8E%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E4%BE%9D%E6%97%A7%E5%8F%AF%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">衍生问题 - 隐藏后页面依旧可访问</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9C%AA%E5%AE%8C%E5%BE%85%E7%BB%AD%E2%80%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">未完待续…</span></a></l